<lb n="0390b03" ed="T"/>金剛手菩薩摩訶薩足故。說自心明曰。</p>
<lb n="0390b04" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0390b0401">唵<note place="inline">引</note>遜婆儞遜婆<note place="inline">一句</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>尾禰<note n="0390004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">踰＝喻【元】【明】</note><note n="0390004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">踰【大】，喻【元】【明】</note><app n="0390004"><lem wit="【大】">踰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】 【明】">喻</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引</note>怛
